        <p class="hs-hero-sub">We cut through the hype, build AI that delivers, and prove value through real results — fast, focused, and tailored to you.</p>
        <div class="hs-hero-actions">
          <a href="https://outlook.office.com/bookwithme/user/f0762b9af6a94ed2add9818a4f3ca4e5@digitaltechnologypartner.ai/meetingtype/qc2lOXjEdkO6GkMS_jZJrQ2?anonymous" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="hs-btn hs-btn-orange">Book a Discovery Call</a>
          <a href="#approach" class="hs-btn hs-btn-ghost">See Our Process →</a>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="hs-hero-right">
        <div class="hs-hero-visual">
          <svg class="hs-topo-svg" viewBox="0 0 400 400" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
            <defs>
